[/list]
[/list]

[b]Result:[/b] meat preparation finally works like a real kitchen.

[h2]What this mod does [b]not[/b] do[/h2]

[list]
[*]No free food
[*]No nutrition buffs
[*]No recipe overrides
[*]No cooking shortcuts
[*]No ‚Äúmerge raw steaks into super-steak‚Äù
[*]No early warnings about poison or sickness
[/list]

If something is unsafe, it stays unsafe.  
If something spoils, it still spoils.

[h2]Design philosophy[/h2]

Kitchen Consolidation follows three rules:

[list=1]
[*][b]Preparation is explicit[/b]  
Nothing is merged automatically.
[*][b]Worst-case safety applies[/b]  
Mixing food never makes it safer.
[*][b]Vanilla systems come first[/b]  
Stews, soups, nutrition, and spoilage all use base-game mechanics.
[/list]

This mod fixes friction ‚Äî not difficulty.

[h2]Compatibility[/h2]

Kitchen Consolidation is designed to be [b]compatibility-first[/b].  
It avoids recipe overrides, global hooks, and invasive patches so it can coexist cleanly with other mods.

